trans-unit.source: Welcome to the SimpleTaskManager for OpenStreetMap

Changes in 1.3.0: New features: More language selection drop-down menusTask list is now sorted by process state Bug fixes: Reduce unnecessary loggingProject creation: Save button enabled but data wasn't completely enteredTask name sometimes not shownRemove unnecessary zoom buttonsFix broken styling of very long notificationsShow task name instead of IDAll kind of errors will now be catched Infrastructure: The server now makes daily database backups Internals: Tasks are now withing the project DTO classAdded swagger UI as better API documentation
